{"tid":2225769,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄧炳強稱警方對暴力分子策略有改變 《警察通例》始終是由警員遵守","createTime":"2020-10-01T14:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:51:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"623e038cdf69b86e68006eabf5d5a8ade428c7a6","tid":2225769,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強接受本台節目《議事論事》訪問時說，近期的抗爭活動，少了「和理非」參與，警方對付暴力分子的策略和部署亦有改變。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強被問到早前修改《警察通例》，有關「傳媒代表」定義的問題，他說警方的修訂獲部分媒體、傳媒工會及學者贊成，警方有聽取意見，但《警察通例》始終是由警員遵守，因此最終都是由警方決定如何修訂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552685-20201001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552685-20201001.htm&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w13ocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=0587a86e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552685-20201001.htm&h=2827c1d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552685-20201001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3c23545783654752aaacac5a965c44d2b2e2bdbd","tid":2225769,"uid":323443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"ec27f45873e14bbf2c8714b17706656535b936c3","tid":2225769,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a89efe3aa7f98b600facef9003e4a298df5be507","tid":2225769,"uid":54125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"本來就無守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n駛咩改嚟改去咁麻煩<br />\n直接淨係寫一句「差佬大晒」咪唔怕啲狗唔識背囉"},{"pid":"84a8ffbf46d370a0bcd1dcd2a6b06673914e86ab","tid":2225769,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c2c954aa962cc76eb091e95c7115f66e844f16c","tid":2225769,"uid":78769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"